(MARY BREATHING HEAVILY)

29:26.080 --> 29:27.070
(SIGHS)

29:28.760 --> 29:30.160
(CLATTER)

29:46.040 --> 29:47.918
- (CARLA GASPS)
- LUCY: Did you find them?

29:48.720 --> 29:50.677
CARLA: Yes, dear. I told you I would.

29:50.840 --> 29:53.559
I don't know why you keep hiding
things in Daddy's office.

29:53.720 --> 29:55.712
You know how he gets
when we touch his things.

29:55.880 --> 29:57.553
LUCY: I know. Where's Mom at?

29:57.720 --> 30:00.076
CARLA: Probably straightening
a painting somewhere.

30:00.240 --> 30:01.071
LUCY: Huh?

30:01.240 --> 30:03.954
CARLA: Come on. Let's go outside
and finish that drawing.

30:04.920 --> 30:08.118
It's too nice outside
to be in this stuffy house.

30:12.440 --> 30:13.590
(THUD)

30:25.160 --> 30:27.231
(TICKING)

30:34.160 --> 30:36.072
(GRUNTING)

30:39.040 --> 30:41.236
(DOORBELL RINGS)

30:42.960 --> 30:45.600
(GASPS) Oh, my God.

30:47.800 --> 30:48.790
MADELINE: Mary?

30:49.840 --> 30:50.876
Mary?

30:52.960 --> 30:53.996
Mary?

30:54.720 --> 30:55.836
Are you in there?

30:56.240 --> 30:58.800
Carla told me you were
futzing around back here.

31:00.480 --> 31:01.755
Mare?

31:02.120 --> 31:04.157
I just need to speak with you
for a moment, dear.

31:04.320 --> 31:06.357
I know you're busy
with the party prep and all.

31:06.520 --> 31:07.636
(KNOCKS)

31:07.840 --> 31:08.910
Mare?

31:09.080 --> 31:10.070
Mary?

31:10.240 --> 31:12.914
Oh, there you are.

31:19.880 --> 31:20.711
Hi, Madeleine.

31:20.880 --> 31:23.759
Hi. Good morning. (GIGGLES)

31:24.520 --> 31:25.920
What are you doing down there?

31:26.480 --> 31:29.640
Oh, I was just, uh... fixing the carpet.

31:30.600 --> 31:34.311
What have you got back there?
Something big for Lucy's birthday, no doubt.

31:34.480 --> 31:36.517
You know Tilly Anderson
from across the street?

31:36.680 --> 31:39.390
They got her daughter Gwinnifer,
that little chubby thing...

31:39.560 --> 31:42.594
They had a designer in Europe
build her a princess coach bed

31:42.760 --> 31:44.877
complete with flat-screen TV built in.

31:45.040 --> 31:47.913
Like she needs to be laying around in front
of the TV any more than she already does.

31:48.080 --> 31:51.351
Poor thing, bless her heart, she's gonna
have a rough go of it come junior high.

31:51.600 --> 31:54.754
I told Tilly she needs to get her into
that new Pilates for preteens class

31:54.920 --> 31:57.952
- over on Fairmont.
- What can I do for you, Madeleine?

31:58.120 --> 32:01.796
Well, it's just I know
that it's Lucy's birthday today,

32:01.960 --> 32:03.952
and I know that my stepdaughters are away

32:04.120 --> 32:06.237
at that new boarding school
in Vermont, you know,

32:06.440 --> 32:08.511
in Sunny Hill. Very exclusive,
very hard to get into.

32:08.680 --> 32:13.634
But it's just the entire neighborhood, it
seems to be talking about this party, so...

32:14.840 --> 32:16.718
Would you like to come
to the party, Madeleine?

32:16.880 --> 32:18.234
Oh! Why, that'd be lovely, dear.

32:18.400 --> 32:19.959
- Thanks so much for the invite.
- Yeah. Okay.

32:20.160 --> 32:22.516
You know, last month,
the Gibsons over on Chestnut...

32:22.680 --> 32:24.000
- No.
- ...they had a deejay,

32:24.160 --> 32:26.038
an entire magic-themed fun house.

32:26.200 --> 32:27.031
Oh, gosh.

32:27.200 --> 32:28.475
Are you doing anything special for Lucy?

32:28.640 --> 32:29.994
It's just her friends and cake.

32:30.160 --> 32:31.310
- Oh.
- So, mm-hmm.

32:31.480 --> 32:33.517
Well, let me know if you
want me to get anything.

32:33.720 --> 32:35.757
It's really no trouble.
There's a designer cupcake place...

32:35.920 --> 32:37.115
MARY: All right, see you in a bit.

32:37.280 --> 32:38.430
MADELINE:
...over by where I get the cats washed.

32:38.600 --> 32:41.718
Okay. Just...
Just let me know. Thanks, dear.

33:08.600 --> 33:10.637
(DOORBELL RINGS)

33:11.720 --> 33:12.949
Fuck.

33:13.760 --> 33:14.955
Oh, Madeleine, for the love of...

33:15.120 --> 33:17.157
(HIP-HOP BEAT PLAYING)

33:17.520 --> 33:18.715
What the...

33:20.040 --> 33:21.838
# Yo #

33:22.000 --> 33:24.276
# I'm the rapping panda,
and I'm here to say #

33:24.480 --> 33:26.631
# Come on, everybody,
