33:33.440 --> 33:35.033
I got, like, three more verses to go.

33:35.240 --> 33:36.754
I'll give you $200 for the suit.

33:36.920 --> 33:38.559
Well, nah, just hit play, and...

33:38.720 --> 33:40.393
I'm not... I'm not Lucy, okay?

33:40.560 --> 33:43.120
Lucy's my daughter,
so you don't have to worry.

33:45.240 --> 33:46.799
I think it's gotta be Lucy.

33:47.000 --> 33:49.515
You're not listening. 300. You want 300?

33:49.680 --> 33:52.714
Ah, there's a down payment on the suit,
and I got a thing this afternoon.

33:52.920 --> 33:54.400
- I...
- $1,000.

33:54.800 --> 33:57.599
$1,000 and two ounces of medical marijuana

33:57.800 --> 33:59.553
from my knee surgery last year.

34:01.600 --> 34:02.636
(DING)

34:04.320 --> 34:05.834
(TICKING)

34:06.000 --> 34:07.434
(SQUEAK)

34:13.000 --> 34:14.911
(PANTING)

34:30.719 --> 34:32.518
- (DOORBELL RINGS)
- LUCY: Mom!

34:32.679 --> 34:34.512
Mom, where are you?

34:34.679 --> 34:36.751
They're here! They're here! They're here!

34:36.920 --> 34:39.594
Come on! Come on! Where are you?

34:39.800 --> 34:41.951
They're here! Party time!

34:45.080 --> 34:46.753
CARLA: Just a minute, darling.

34:46.920 --> 34:48.070
I'm coming.

